      "type": "markdown",
      "id": "144e1a47bbb14e58",
      "text": "Regulating DAOs - Schneier on Security, [no date]. Online. [Accessed 24 October 2022]. Available from: https://www.schneier.com/blog/archives/2022/10/regulating-daos.html\n\n"
